The '''green jery''' ('''''Neomixis viridis''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Cisticolidae]].
It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Madagascar]].

Its natural [[habitat]] is [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]].

